# XORS Brand Identity

Design system derived from ark.studio/xors wireframes.

## Color Palette

- **Stone** `#B5B5B5` — primary background
- **Ink** `#0A0A0A` — dark sections, primary buttons, text
- **Cream** `#F5F2ED` — content surfaces (examples, modals, forms)
- **Gold** `#C8A843` — accent color (status badges, focus rings, highlights)
- **Never use orange.** The old `#ff6b00` accent is deprecated.

## Typography

- **Body/prose**: `Source Serif 4` — editorial, literary tone
- **UI/labels**: `Inter` — buttons, nav, form labels, section headings
- **Code/mono**: `JetBrains Mono` — status badges, technical labels
- All text is **lowercase** (`text-transform: lowercase` on `html`)

## Layout Principles

- **No border-radius** — all interactive elements are square (0px)
- Generous whitespace — sections padded 100-120px vertically
- Gray ↔ black section transitions for contrast
- Pill-shaped footer (`border-radius: 999px`, ink bg, cream text)
- Two-column legal pages: title pinned left, body flows right then single-column

## Component Patterns

- Cards: `rgba(255,255,255,0.15)` on stone, `rgba(255,255,255,0.03)` on ink
- Section numbers in gold mono (`01`, `02`, `03`) with divider line
- Status badges: mono font, 1px border, no fill
- Focus rings use gold: `outline: 2px solid #C8A843`
- Links underlined with `text-underline-offset: 3px`, gold on hover
